<br>
Offhand is ratio only.  Procs maybe, if you want to rely on procs.<br>
<br>
Mainhand is a combination of delay and ratio, ratio is obvious, and delay starts to rule with really fast weapons because of the mainhand levelbased damage bonus.  Bigger damage stat though will effect backstabs, so it's a tradeoff you have to play with.<br>
<br>
Backstab recycle speed indeed has absolutely nothing to do with the delay of your weapons.  I backstab just as often weilding a 30 delay weapon as I do with a 21 delay weapon, assuming I have the same haste items/spells for each. <p>Tenbil En`Haldar<br>
Scout and Garden Tool of the 51st Season<br>
